  "menu": {
    "intro": "Great food, good company — that's what it's all about. Allergen key: 1 Cereals, 2 Crustaceans, 3 Eggs, 4 Fish, 5 Peanuts, 6 Soybeans, 7 Milk, 8 Nuts, 9 Celery, 10 Mustard, 11 Sesame Seeds, 12 Sulphur Dioxide & Sulphates, 13 Lupin, 14 Molluscs.",
